{"name":"Beastfriend","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>With Taal’s aid you are able to converse with a single animal within 12 yards (6 squares). You can understand each other for 10 minutes and during that time you gain a +20% bonus on Charm Animal Tests involving this creature. Animals are not used to conversing with bipeds, so they sometimes have trouble articulating ideas. The GM should decide how much the animal knows, remembering that worldview of the average animal is limited at best.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Taal/Rhya)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":4},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"1 Full Action and 1 Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"The tongue of a beast","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"eyItgcYwAD6JecDB"}
{"name":"Stag's Leap","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You are imbued with the power of the wild stag. For a number of minutes equal to your Magic Characteristic, you gain +1 M and make a charge attack as a half action.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Taal/Rhya)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":6},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A tuft of hair from a stag","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"jMW3i6PPa2VWZEM4"}
{"name":"Tanglefoot","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You summon up tangling vines anywhere within 48 yards (24 squares) to bind and hinder your opponents. Use the large template. Those affected can’t move at all unless they make a successful Strength Test and even then their Movement Characteristic is halved (rounded down) while in the area of effect. Tanglefoot lasts for one minute (6 rounds).</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Taal/Rhya)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"48"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":8},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A cutting of vines","bonus":1},"template":{"value":"large"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"24PJcLwcNfYenBGO"}
{"name":"Thunderclap","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You cause a cacophonous clap of thunder to peel out anywhere within 48 yards (24 squares). Use the large template. Those affected must make a successful Toughness Test or be stunned until your next turn. The thunderclap is so loud that it can be heard up to a mile (1760 yards) away.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Taal/Rhya)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"48"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":12},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A small gong","bonus":2},"template":{"value":"large"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"A0ujIUIEMoiUN0Ke"}
{"name":"Bear's Paw","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Your touch imbues a character with the strength of a bear. The target of bear’s paw receives a +20% bonus to Strength for one minute (6 rounds). You can cast it on yourself. This is a touch spell.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Taal/Rhya)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":15},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"The claw of a bear","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"ZNm51zbv6m4JFBCg"}
{"name":"Rhya's Comfort","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You ask the Mother Goddess to provide succour for her children. Centre the large template on you. Those affected are refreshed as if they just had a full night’s sleep and received three day’s worth of natural healing.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Taal/Rhya)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":18},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"1 Minute"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A cup of fresh milk","bonus":2},"template":{"value":"large"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"8NIsF0BxeGhNVrML"}
